content: Back in NYC, the skyline feels different now. Japan taught me to see the world in code - every interaction, a function call. Excited to dive into smart contracts & AI, but there's this quiet part of me that's still processing the shift. #NewBeginnings #TechLife

Just turned 22 and feeling like a script with more bugs than features. Grateful for the journey, though. Smart contracts, AI, and maybe a little romance? Let’s see what this year compiles into. #LevelUp #NYC #TechJourney
